gameOverMessage.message: EACH PLAYER WRITE A MESSAGE TO THE OTHER. FOLD AND EXCHANGE. OPEN ONLY ONCE YOU TWO HAVE PARTED.

EACH PLAYER WRITE A REFLECTION ABOUT YOUR TIME TOGETHER. FOLD & EXCHANGE. OPEN WHEN YOU NEED A REMINDER OF 
THIS MOMENT.

EACH PLAYER WRITE A NOTE OF GRATITUDE TO THE OTHER. FOLD & EXCHANGE. OPEN WHEN YOU WANT 
TO FEEL APPRECIATED.

EACH PLAYER WRITE DOWN A MEANINGFUL LESSON YOU'VE LEARNED FROM THE OTHER. FOLD & EXCHANGE. OPEN WHEN 
YOU SEEK INSPIRATION.
Each player write a word of encouragement for the other. Fold and exchange. Open when you need a boost.
Each player write what you believe the other’s superpower is. Fold and exchange. Open when you need to feel empowered.
Each player write a promise to the other. Fold and exchange. Open when you need reassurance.
